videos.headline: Cardano-Hillary hustles for the steal and the bucket
videos.description: Indiana's Nicole Cardano-Hillary rushes in for the steal and fights off Raina Perez to score.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cardano-Hillary hustles for the steal and the bucket) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hoosiers, Wolfpack trade quick baskets
videos.description: Indiana's Grace Berger drops jumper to tie things up then NC State's Raina Perez quickly responds with a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hoosiers, Wolfpack trade quick baskets) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cardano-Hillary bodies her way into an and-1 bucket
videos.description: Indiana's Nicole Cardano-Hillary comes off the fast break pass from Grace Berger and drives in for the bucket while drawing the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cardano-Hillary bodies her way into an and-1 bucket) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Perez's jumper inches NC State closer to the Hooisers
videos.description: Raina Perez drains the fadeaway jumper as she brings her team within 2 of the Indiana lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Perez's jumper inches NC State closer to the Hooisers) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana survives vs. NC State to advance to their first ever Elite Eight
videos.description: NC State's Elissa Cunane misses the chance at tying up the game and Indiana pulls off the upset to advance.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Indiana survives vs. NC State to advance to their first ever Elite Eight) 2021/3/27 ESHEET
